Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.74,0:54:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As intellectualization, does it make any difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.22,0:54:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Does reality make any difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.07,0:55:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you only live one instant at a time anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.11,0:55:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so it doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.59,0:55:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't live a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.03,0:55:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only live this instant right here and now, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.70,0:55:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.76,0:55:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there events where atrocities are visited on a population
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.14,0:55:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,where there hasn't been a previous karmic connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.92,0:55:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.66,0:55:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of these things I would have to research out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.18,0:55:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say there's probably such a thing as collective karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.46,0:55:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.04,0:55:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably such a thing as collective karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.38,0:55:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, a whole nation has to take responsibility that it committed to that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.62,0:55:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a basic violation of human ethics, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.30,0:55:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would imagine a whole nation that's committed, you know, made a serious error will probably
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.28,0:55:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in some kind of a national sense have to undo that in some other way perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.44,0:55:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That would just be my inner sense of it, but I haven't researched it out necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.12,0:56:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Well, we've answered all the questions that have puzzled Van Zandt since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.51,0:56:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done it for all eternity, and that's a good afternoon's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.27,0:56:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.61,0:56:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.28,0:56:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
